readme:
Service Usage

The service is initiated when clinic data that has been identified as being shared between eMedical and the back end system is added / updated / removed.
(New or changed clinic, clinic contact details, change in details of services provided by clinic, or clinic 5CC status)
The back end system will either create a new clinic or apply the advised changes to the relevant back-end clinic structure.
Asynchronous service.
